summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4333 for the improvement of the alley, blocks 29 and 30, Law's 2nd Addition, being the alley between 5th Avenue West and 6th Avenue West, from West Garfield Street to West Blaine Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 51376, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
